data.description: Introducing a charming and well-maintained property located in the popular Camelot neighborhood. This lovely home offers a range of appealing features that make it an ideal choice for buyers seeking comfort and convenience.  Step inside and you'll immediately notice the beautiful ceramic tile flooring that adds a touch of elegance to the main living areas. The open layout creates a sense of spaciousness, making it perfect for both entertaining and everyday living. The neutral colors throughout the house create a cozy and inviting atmosphere.  The kitchen is a highlight of this home, featuring stainless steel appliances and a tasteful backsplash that complements the flooring. Whether you're cooking for yourself or hosting friends and family, this kitchen will meet all your needs.   One of the standout features of this property is the large yard and huge covered patio, complete with a built-in BBQ grill. This outdoor space is perfect for enjoying the great weather and hosting gatherings with loved ones. The absence of a neighbor next door provides added privacy and tranquility.  Convenience is key with this home's proximity to major highways and shopping centers, making commuting and running errands a breeze. The spacious driveway offers ample parking space for multiple vehicles, which is a great benefit for busy households.  The updated bathrooms feature modern fixtures and finishes, adding a touch of luxury to your daily routine. Ceiling fans in every room ensure comfort and energy efficiency throughout the year.  Situated on a quiet street and surrounded by mature trees, this property offers a peaceful and serene environment. Whether you're relaxing on the patio or taking a stroll through the neighborhood, you'll feel right at home.  Don't miss the chance to make this wonderful property yours. With its desirable features, convenient location, and well-maintained condition, this home is sure to impress. Schedule a private showing today and discover the perfect place to call home!
